entries.arrival_phase_1: pcontrast3 RSF Command: < pcontrast1 We are tracking the Black Sun Ace now, stand by for an uplink of his location. pcontrast3 >
entries.arrival_phase_2: pcontrast3 RSF Command: < pcontrast1 Waypoint uploaded, take him down. pcontrast3 >
entries.assassinate_success: pcontrast3 RSF Command: < pcontrast1 The sortie is a success, nice shooting. pcontrast3 >
entries.destroy_escort: pcontrast3 RSF Command: < pcontrast1 Don't forget his wingmen, we want them all removed. pcontrast3 >
entries.escort_remaining: pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < pcontrast1 An escorting craft has been destroyed, %DI remain. pcontrast3 >
entries.escort_wiped_out: pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < pcontrast1 All escorting craft have been destroyed. pcontrast3 >
entries.failed_escape: pcontrast3 RSF Command: < pcontrast1 You let him escape to plague us still. pcontrast3 >
entries.quest_escort_d: A group of Black Sun Pirates, these must be destroyed as well.
entries.quest_target_d: A known Black Sun pirate wing leader
entries.split_quest_alert: pcontrast3 Capt Dinge: < pcontrast1 You appear to have hit a little snag out there Captain.  Get patched up and take down that Ace. pcontrast3 >
entries.split_quest_alert_fail: pcontrast3 Capt Dinge: < pcontrast1 You appear to have hit a little snag out there Captain.  Get patched up and take down that Ace. pcontrast3 >
entries.title: Naboo System: Destroy the Black Sun Ace
entries.title_d: Eliminate a dangerous Black Sun Ace Fighter. When you complete this mission, return to Captain Dinge in the Theed Palace and Captain Dinge will train you in a new Pilot skill.
